name: Isaac Donovan
description: I am not concerned with having tons of friends. A few good friends is all I need. I do not always follow the mass, but there is always something to learn from what is being seen and heard. My perceptions may not always be right but both good and evil can come out from one very thing and the question is what will be your reactions towards both results – a sign of maturity. I am unique in that I will not waste time with “shallow” interactions. I am only open to meaningful, honest, and exclusive relationships with like minded people. My late mom taught me not cry over spilled milk. I enjoy been original, creative, highly imaginative and rediscovering all that life has to offer. I am open to new ideas.
